## File Naming Conventions

### Components
```
PascalCase.tsx           # React components
PascalCase.styles.ts     # Styled components (if separated)
PascalCase.test.tsx      # Component tests
```

### Services/Utilities
```
camelCase.service.ts     # Services
camelCase.utils.ts       # Utilities
camelCase.types.ts       # Type definitions
```

### Configuration
```
kebab-case.config.ts     # Configuration files
```

## Import Order
```typescript
// 1. React/React Native
import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import { View, Text, TouchableOpacity } from 'react-native';

// 2. Third-party libraries
import { useNavigation } from '@react-navigation/native';
import { ethers } from 'ethers';

// 3. Internal modules (absolute imports)
import { useWalletStore } from '@/store/useWalletStore';
import { WalletCard } from '@/components/wallet/WalletCard';

// 4. Relative imports
import { styles } from './HomeScreen.styles';
import { formatBalance } from './utils';

// 5. Types (last)
import type { Transaction } from '@/types';
```

## Module Boundaries

### Backend Modules
Each module should be self-contained:
```
modules/wallet/
├── wallet.module.ts      # Module definition
├── wallet.controller.ts  # HTTP endpoints
├── wallet.service.ts     # Business logic
├── wallet.repository.ts  # Data access (optional)
├── dto/                  # Request/Response DTOs
├── entities/             # Database entities
└── tests/                # Module tests
```

### Mobile Features
Group by feature for larger features:
```
screens/send/
├── SendScreen.tsx
├── components/
│   ├── AmountInput.tsx
│   └── RecipientSelector.tsx
├── hooks/
│   └── useSendTransaction.ts
└── utils/
    └── validation.ts
```

## Path Aliases
```json
// tsconfig.json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "baseUrl": ".",
    "paths": {
      "@/*": ["src/*"],
      "@components/*": ["src/components/*"],
      "@screens/*": ["src/screens/*"],
      "@services/*": ["src/services/*"],
      "@hooks/*": ["src/hooks/*"],
      "@utils/*": ["src/utils/*"],
      "@types/*": ["src/types/*"]
    }
  }
}
```
